KPM (Kapuletu Project Manager)
Product Workflow Specification
This document describes the complete operational workflow of KPM from the moment an organization joins the platform until software is successfully released.

The Story of KPM
Imagine a company called Acme Technologies.
They have just subscribed to KPM.
They want to build three software products.
